   "body" : "Avoid undefined behaviour in:\r\n* `EstimateMedianVal` (policy)\r\n* `ConnectTip` (validation)\r\n* `CreateTransaction` (wallet)\r\n\r\nThese are real nontheoretical UB cases in the sense that they are easily reachable.\r\n\r\nAs soon as this PR is merged I'll make sure we get our UBSAN (`-fsanitize=undefined`) job to run also run `test/functional/test_runner.py`. UBSAN in Travis running the test suite would have catched all three of these. Again showing the value of automated testing as a complement to our thorough human reviewing :-)\r\n\r\nSteps to reproduce:\r\n\r\n```\r\n./configure --with-sanitizers=undefined && make check && ./test/functional/test_runner.py\r\n```",
